User Stories:

A user should be able to log in 
A user should be able to choose and successfully log in with their facebook account
A user should have their avatar automatically assigned (via gravitar)
A user should be able to search by team name
A user should be able to view that teams page
A user should be able to comment on that teams page ]
A user should be able to view pictures from that teams arena 
A user should be able to view all comments for that specific team

Icebox:
A user should be able to view comments and stadium location on a map
